That means you would owe the bank money and might face big fines and potential jail time. You're right - banks WON'T give you twice the money. Even if you're able to deposit the check a second time, that's fraud and the bank will find out in a day or two. And then you'll be on the hook for it. Fraud includes you trying to play the bank by depositing a check on your phone and at the bank. Don't do it!
